title: NJ Senate president Steve Sweeney speaks out after loss to Edward Durr, GOP newcomer
author: FOX 29 Philadelphia
description:
Edward Durr, a furniture company truck driver and first-time officeholder, defeated Steve Sweeney in New Jersey’s 3rd Legislative District, according to results tallied Thursday.
